reviewText: I rated this three stars even though I have not actually seen it! Reason is to remind possible purchasers that it is in PAL format and thus will not be seen by viewers in the USA. Our players do not recognize PAL. Otherwise, given the three performers listed it ought to be a wonderful dvd...in the right regions.
While Nancy is good as usual the standout of the three performers is the Richard Thompson set. Makes this hard to find disc worth seeking out!
